biweekly.property

Class TimezoneUrl

  • java.lang.Object
    • biweekly.property.ICalProperty
      • biweekly.property.ValuedProperty<String>
        • biweekly.property.TextProperty
          • biweekly.property.TimezoneUrl

  • public class TimezoneUrl
extends TextProperty

    Defines a URL that points to an iCalendar object that contains further information on a timezone.

    Code sample: 

     VTimezone timezone = ...
 timezone.setTimezoneUrl("http://example.com/tz.ics");

    Author:
    Michael Angstadt
    See Also:
    RFC 5545 p.106, RFC 2445 p.101
